1
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,600
{\an8}Has your dad ever told you
about any cases at all?

2
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:49,600
{\an8}Perhaps one about a family
that was murdered ten years ago?

3
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:56,280
{\an8}Taiga! Mr. Naruban was poisoned.

4
00:02:57,200 --> 00:03:00,560
{\an8}You've been through a lot, Naruban.
Soon, your duty will be over,

5
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,000
{\an8}and you'll take a long break.

6
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,640
That's right.

7
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:13,960
Hey! Come quick!

8
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:16,640
- The MV is out.
- Wow, so handsome.

9
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:19,360
Wow, he's cute when he does that.

10
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:21,160
- Ryu's so cute!
- Share it.

11
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,600
Everyone has to see this.

12
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:29,200
- Wow, so good!
- Share the song now!

13
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,120
- Here we go.
- He's back!

14
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,760
Share it!

15
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,280
So adorable!

16
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:38,160
Give me the song.

17
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,600
Hey, look!

18
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,960
- What should I do?
- Ryu! So cool!

19
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,920
- He's so cool.
- I wanna hug him!

20
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:01,000
Quick, let me take a photo too!

21
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:06,240
Ms. Atinuch , why is Ryu here
at the building right now?

22
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,360
Yes!

23
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:18,959
Excuse me. Can we switch?

24
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,279
Can I join in for a picture?

25
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:22,560
Can I get a quick photo?

26
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,280
Can I take a photo?

27
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:30,280
Can I get a quick photo?

28
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:37,600
Rin, can you help get Ryu upstairs?

29
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,320
- Who is that?
- Ryu! Ryu Dragon!

30
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:31,680
People downstairs said Ryu Dragon is here!

31
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,800
Step back. I'm going down to see!

32
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,160
You can take it from here, Ms. Nuch.

33
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:45,760
Wait, which department do you work in?

34
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:49,480
Don't bother remembering.
I'm on my last day.

35
00:05:57,920 --> 00:06:01,200
Mr. Ryu, please follow me
to the lounge, this way.

36
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,960
What's that woman's name?

37
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,120
Don't worry about her.

38
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,800
This way, please.

39
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:26,880
If I let an employee
who walked out keep working,

40
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,480
who would respect me, Mr. Taiga?

41
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:35,000
I can't just bend the rules
to satisfy one person.

42
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,480
Then I'll take responsibility too,

43
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,840
since I went with Rin.

44
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:52,800
Is one employee really worth that much?

45
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:00,680
I see everyone as equally valuable.

46
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:04,160
You don't have to break your own rules.

47
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:06,760
Just uphold them the way you want.

48
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:14,400
Don't you care how much this upsets me?

49
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,120
I'm sorry.

50
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:26,440
Okay, Rin can come back to work here.

51
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:36,320
Ryu! Ryu!

52
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,840
- Ryu!
- Is Ryu coming down?!

53
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,880
- Is Ryu with you?
- Ryu!

54
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:48,480
<i>Hurry up! Someone's waiting.</i>

55
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,920
Ryu's so cute.

56
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:23,440
You'll be Mr. Ryu Dragon's bodyguard

57
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:25,920
for the entire time he's in Thailand.

58
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:29,560
I've never looked after an artist before.
I don't think I'm fit for it.

59
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:33,159
You're perfect.
I've seen your skills already.

60
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:40,919
Mr. Ryu has Thai heritage.
He speaks and understands Thai perfectly.

61
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:46,480
I really'm not good at this. Excuse me.

62
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:49,240
We'll find a professional
security team instead.

63
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,840
I want to talk to you.

64
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,760
Sorry, I'm busy.

65
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:23,240
Rin, wait for me in the room.

66
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:33,960
Is this your boss?

67
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:39,240
But Ms. Nun said you could work for me.

68
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,360
Rin only works with people
she's comfortable with.

69
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,320
But it's an executive order.

70
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,680
I work for Hi app.

71
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,520
I need someone who can take care of me.

72
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:56,720
You should hire a professional.

73
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,000
You want to take care of an artist?

74
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:24,280
It could be fun.

75
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:29,080
I'm an artist too.

76
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:39,960
You need to be careful, Rin.
I still don't know

77
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:42,320
who put Mr. Naruban in a coma.

78
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,920
Who do you suspect?

79
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:51,080
I have to find them.

80
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:12,120
Mr. Taiga is our designer.

81
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:15,280
Whatever look you want,

82
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:18,240
Mr. Taiga can prepare it for you.

83
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:25,360
Mr. Ryu.

84
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:43,240
I have my own stylist.
If I can't use my own people,

85
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:46,120
I won't take this job.

86
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:49,320
Well, we've already promoted it
that you will perform

87
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:51,440
at the Hi app launch.

88
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:55,720
VIP seats are fully booked,
and all event tickets are gone.

89
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:12,480
Wait.

90
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:18,560
No woman's ever run away
from me like you did.

91
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:24,520
I'm not into stuff like this.
Sorry, I don't know how famous you are.

92
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:26,640
Try searching.

93
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:30,200
Or search the tag, Hong Kong.
That's my hometown.

94
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,640
Give me your phone.

95
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,960
I'll show you.

96
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:55,280
This is my personal number. Call anytime.

97
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:01,720
Wait!

98
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:04,760
Don't delete it.

99
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:21,160
Don't be mad yet, Aru.

100
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:25,800
I went to the warehouse. They told me,
because I really wanted to see you.

101
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:31,200
Can I come in and talk inside?

102
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:58,640
If you have something to say, say it.

103
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:04,360
I'm not free.
I have a live sale in half an hour.

104
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:15,960
I miss you.

105
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:24,440
Got it. That's it, right?

106
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:01,680
You bastard! You jerk!

107
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,560
Pat! Don't!

108
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:17,280
- Pat!
- You two teamed up to trick me!

109
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:19,680
- Pat, stop!
- Let me go!

110
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:21,640
Go away! Shameless!

111
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:32,280
Who are you?

112
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,640
Lee?

113
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,640
I'm not Lee, or whoever that is.

114
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:44,520
Don't come back here,
if you don't want to die. Get out!

115
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:50,320
That's enough, Pat.

116
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,920
Don't look, Rin.

117
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:19,320
Don't look at a fool like me.

118
00:17:34,320 --> 00:17:35,320
Hey.

119
00:17:36,880 --> 00:17:40,000
Te, do you want something to eat?
I can make it for you.

120
00:17:42,280 --> 00:17:44,360
Have you gone to visit Dad yet?

121
00:17:52,920 --> 00:17:54,640
You're not Dad's real child.

122
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:05,640
Whoa, Nun!

123
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:08,160
Nun, don't do this to your brother.

124
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:12,320
He's not my brother!
He's the troublemaker in our family.

125
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,400
- Te!
- Hey.

126
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:18,440
Dad hasn't even gone yet,
you're already trying to take everything?

127
00:18:18,520 --> 00:18:20,400
Don't hurt your sister. Let go.

128
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:26,360
Nun!

129
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,360
This little thing won't kill me.

130
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:31,640
I'm not going to let you die so easily.

131
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:34,320
Just a few scars on your face,
four or five should do.

132
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:38,200
Film it and show it to any woman.
That's way more satisfying.

133
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:42,040
- Nun, don't!
- If you can't stay quiet,

134
00:18:42,120 --> 00:18:43,560
then get out!

135
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:46,120
Don't drag your name
through 3C Corp. I'm building.

136
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:47,680
3C Corp. you're building?

137
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:50,520
You dare compare yourself to Dad?

138
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:59,640
Nun, let it go.

139
00:19:11,120 --> 00:19:14,960
Why cry, Mom? Tears don't help.

140
00:19:18,040 --> 00:19:20,240
Only standing up and fighting

141
00:19:21,360 --> 00:19:23,360
will make life truly yours.

142
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:33,240
This year, we're planning an event,

143
00:19:33,320 --> 00:19:34,840
Super Global App.

144
00:19:39,360 --> 00:19:40,840
First up,

145
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:44,040
a uniform makeover
by the renowned Japanese designer

146
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:45,880
Mr. Taiga.

147
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:47,800
Next up

148
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:50,440
is a concert by Mr. Ryu Dragon,

149
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:54,120
the idol from Hong Kong,
livestreaming fun to the world

150
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:56,320
through the Hi app.

151
00:20:05,040 --> 00:20:07,160
I'll send the files
of the songs I perform.

152
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:09,960
Everyone on the team must be my people.

153
00:20:12,080 --> 00:20:15,320
I want to know who's in the VIP seats,

154
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:18,440
where my official fan club sits,

155
00:20:20,280 --> 00:20:21,400
and most importantly,

156
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,280
I need VVIP-level care

157
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:27,080
throughout the work here.

158
00:20:29,840 --> 00:20:33,360
We understand the requirements.
We'll arrange everything accordingly.

159
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:35,560
Anything else?

160
00:20:43,520 --> 00:20:46,760
It's my show. I'm using my own team.

161
00:20:47,600 --> 00:20:50,400
No clothes or accessories
from anyone else,

162
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,880
not a single piece.

163
00:20:57,840 --> 00:21:00,560
I'm handling the 3C Corp. uniforms
because I want to.

164
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:03,640
I'm not working on the concert.

165
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:05,960
And if I had to,

166
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:07,800
I'd have to refuse.

167
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:26,160
Alright, that's settled.

168
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:28,440
The two events won't be combined.

169
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:31,520
Separate events, separate promotion.

170
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:35,400
Everyone, please enjoy

171
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:37,880
some snacks and tea
in the lounge, this way.

172
00:21:39,240 --> 00:21:40,360
This way, please.

173
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:44,880
After you.

174
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:38,760
I'm flying back today.
You can handle the rest with my assistant.

175
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,960
That's so on-brand.

176
00:22:52,040 --> 00:22:55,080
Ryu Dragon, the bad boy idol.

177
00:23:07,120 --> 00:23:08,720
YOUNG COP TAKES BRIBES
CHASING QUICK RICHES

178
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:10,600
YOUNG OFFICER KHANIN CAUGHT
IN HUMAN TRAFFICKING NETWORK

179
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:28,920
Are you sure about this information,
Dhammatat?

180
00:23:30,840 --> 00:23:33,000
I never mess up on intel.

181
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:39,320
Khanin is a cop
tied to a human trafficking gang.

182
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,360
Then he got fired.

183
00:23:42,040 --> 00:23:44,480
He was your mom's ex

184
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:47,600
before she married a businessman,

185
00:23:48,280 --> 00:23:50,280
Prin, your father.

186
00:23:56,320 --> 00:23:59,120
Khanin is a member of Fire Phoenix,

187
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,720
just like Naruban.

188
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:30,080
Let's go.

189
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:16,320
NARUBAN ASAWAWONG

190
00:25:50,280 --> 00:25:51,480
Dad, are you faking being sick?

191
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:56,960
I just want to know who's really my enemy.

192
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:32,320
Now you see who you can trust

193
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:34,560
and who you need
to get rid of immediately.

194
00:26:35,520 --> 00:26:39,040
Yes. Nun always tries to take your place.

195
00:26:39,120 --> 00:26:40,880
You have to prove everything.

196
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:44,360
Show everyone clearly
that you're the superior one.

197
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:34,280
BRUTAL KILLING, YOUNG 3C CO-FOUNDER
SHOT MULTIPLE TIMES

198
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:35,760
THREE SONS MISSING

199
00:28:00,080 --> 00:28:03,800
Naruban, Khanin, and Prin

200
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:06,920
are members of Fire Phoenix.

201
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:23,400
I visited Naruban.

202
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:27,960
He's not sick! He's fooling all of us.
His son's the one in charge of everything.

203
00:28:31,560 --> 00:28:32,880
Not Nunnapat?

204
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:37,640
His daughter? Why?

205
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:43,080
Why doesn't Fire Phoenix
let women hold power?

206
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:46,600
I don't know!
You think I'm part of Fire Phoenix?

207
00:28:48,280 --> 00:28:49,520
No.

208
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:53,200
I just thought you might know
more than me.

209
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,680
Ryu Dragon fan meet tickets.

210
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:25,520
None.

211
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:33,320
What about photos?
Autographs? The pen he used,

212
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:36,080
or a cup he drank from,
even a tissue would do.

213
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:38,080
You've got to give me something!

214
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:39,960
There's nothing.

215
00:29:40,040 --> 00:29:42,320
- Take that!
- Ow!

216
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:43,920
No way!

217
00:29:44,720 --> 00:29:48,040
No way! How could you
forget your friend like this?

218
00:29:48,120 --> 00:29:49,120
- Did you hide it?
- Well.

219
00:29:49,200 --> 00:29:51,000
- Did you hide it?
- Really, there's nothing.

220
00:29:51,080 --> 00:29:52,560
Where did you put it? Tell me!

221
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:54,120
- Where did you put it?
- You won't find it.

222
00:30:04,320 --> 00:30:05,720
Are you feeling better now?

223
00:30:07,800 --> 00:30:09,200
Still a bit weak.

224
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:11,600
Good that it wasn't serious.

225
00:30:12,760 --> 00:30:15,280
You probably thought
I was on the verge of death.

226
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:17,880
Well, I didn't know.

227
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:21,360
When I got to the hospital,
you didn't look well.

228
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:27,120
Nun, it's good
that your father's recovering now.

229
00:30:30,080 --> 00:30:31,040
I want to go home.

230
00:30:32,440 --> 00:30:37,120
I think you should stay here a bit longer
and get checked.

231
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,800
You're still not fully recovered.

232
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:41,160
I'm going home.

233
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:49,480
Let's go. I'll take you home.

234
00:31:26,440 --> 00:31:27,920
The person who must die,

235
00:31:29,360 --> 00:31:30,520
Taiga.

236
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,760
Are you feeling better now?

237
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:42,120
Yeah.

238
00:31:43,520 --> 00:31:46,120
I can't stay in the hospital too long.

239
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,480
I'm worried about work.

240
00:31:48,600 --> 00:31:50,440
What did the doctor say?

241
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:56,640
Same as before,
stress and not enough rest.

242
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:05,240
Good that it wasn't serious.

243
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:10,000
Seeing you reminded me of my father.

244
00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:18,120
He never got sick.

245
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:24,400
Until one moment of pain took his life.

246
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,680
I'm sorry to hear that.

247
00:32:29,080 --> 00:32:30,320
You know?

248
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:35,880
Death is closer than we think.

249
00:32:37,760 --> 00:32:40,400
So close that sometimes
you don't even notice

250
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:43,360
which direction the strike will come from.

251
00:32:45,320 --> 00:32:47,200
Only cowards

252
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:50,240
get shaken by the word "death".

253
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:56,520
But my father always said death

254
00:32:58,080 --> 00:33:00,480
is the fairest judgment.

255
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:09,080
I don't agree with your father.

256
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:15,680
Words are the real judgment.

257
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:19,600
Words can build someone,

258
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:21,800
destroy someone,

259
00:33:23,080 --> 00:33:24,840
even crush a person alive.

260
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:35,600
Coffee, sir.

261
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:51,760
You came at the perfect time.

262
00:33:51,840 --> 00:33:55,520
You can call me anytime.
I was waiting outside the room.

263
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:08,239
You're close with Taiga, right?

264
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:11,639
No, I'm not.

265
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:16,159
I've seen Nun get annoyed
about you and Taiga.

266
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:21,280
It's nothing. I'm just doing my job.

267
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:28,520
Then I have one more task for you.

268
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:34,239
Don't tell me you're secretly complaining
that I'm giving you too much to do.

269
00:34:35,080 --> 00:34:38,320
No, I'm happy to do it for 3C Corp.

270
00:34:39,239 --> 00:34:41,120
You can give me orders anytime.

271
00:34:44,199 --> 00:34:45,920
Besides looking after me,

272
00:34:46,639 --> 00:34:51,320
I want you to keep an eye on Taiga
and report everything he does.

273
00:34:52,679 --> 00:34:57,200
I'll make sure you get close to him.
Don't worry about what Nun thinks.

274
00:35:00,640 --> 00:35:01,920
Yes, sir.

275
00:35:43,240 --> 00:35:45,280
My job is to observe,

276
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:47,160
manage, and take care
of everything perfectly.

277
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:53,480
Your person is such a mess.

278
00:35:56,160 --> 00:35:59,360
- I had Rin handle it myself.
- But it's not her job.

279
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:01,960
It is!

280
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:07,320
Because it's a task I assigned.
You like that designer.

281
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:10,920
You're crazy about him
and would do anything to keep him.

282
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:15,600
You've never cared, never even noticed?

283
00:36:15,680 --> 00:36:18,560
Since he came to 3C Corp.,
it's been nothing but trouble.

284
00:36:18,640 --> 00:36:21,840
But all of that is because of Te,
not because of Taiga.

285
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:24,120
You'd still favor an outsider?

286
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:28,480
You could trade an executive position
just for one man, Nun.

287
00:36:29,160 --> 00:36:32,360
I can always promote
someone more suitable,

288
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:33,920
because I don't play favorites.

289
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:37,720
I only care about the work
and the profits 3C Corp. will make.

290
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,160
What do you think you're doing?

291
00:36:52,120 --> 00:36:53,840
Even with my father backing you,

292
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:56,800
don't think I can't find a way
to get rid of you.

293
00:37:03,640 --> 00:37:05,640
I've caused you trouble again, haven't I?

294
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:12,040
I'm fine. Don't overthink it.

295
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:22,720
You're full, your brain's probably racing.
Better go back to work on the uniforms,

296
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:24,000
Mr. Designer.

297
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:45,800
Check out the photos I sent
and bring her to me.

298
00:37:45,880 --> 00:37:48,280
I want to talk to this girl privately.

299
00:38:26,400 --> 00:38:27,400
Quick!

300
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:36,360
Hey! What are you doing?

301
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:43,680
Help! Somebody help!

302
00:38:46,040 --> 00:38:47,480
Hey, don't come any closer!

303
00:38:47,560 --> 00:38:49,000
- What are you doing?
- Run!

304
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:52,680
- Are you okay?
- Aru!

305
00:38:53,840 --> 00:38:55,120
Aru!

306
00:39:12,600 --> 00:39:13,640
Hello.

307
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:15,640
What?

308
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:18,640
Just one woman and you couldn't catch her?

309
00:39:19,200 --> 00:39:21,840
Did your parents even give you a brain?

310
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,600
Aru.

311
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:11,640
This is your mom's house.

312
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:13,320
Sit down first.

313
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:29,720
Mom isn't home.
She took my sister to the doctor.

314
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:34,760
I didn't know where else to take you,
so I brought you here.

315
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:39,760
But what were you doing there?

316
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:42,960
I…

317
00:40:43,880 --> 00:40:45,360
I missed you, Aru.

318
00:40:46,320 --> 00:40:48,080
I just wanted to see you

319
00:40:49,040 --> 00:40:50,960
and apologize.

320
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,000
Aru.

321
00:40:57,840 --> 00:40:59,520
Can you just listen to me this once?

322
00:41:00,680 --> 00:41:02,320
And I won't hold onto you anymore.

323
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:04,880
Please.

324
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:08,120
This house is mortgaged.

325
00:41:08,920 --> 00:41:10,360
But I'll take care of everything.

326
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:12,240
Thank you so much, Miss Pat.

327
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:16,920
No worries. We're family, after all.
We take care of each other.

328
00:41:24,040 --> 00:41:25,720
Miss Pat must be really kind

329
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:29,000
to your mom and sister, right?

330
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:38,520
I can never repay Miss Pat for anything.

331
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:45,040
Except with your own body.

332
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:51,040
But honestly,
she's kind of pitiful too, Aru.

333
00:41:57,280 --> 00:41:59,240
Because you're the only one

334
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:01,880
always by her side,

335
00:42:02,520 --> 00:42:04,320
following her wishes,

336
00:42:05,080 --> 00:42:07,640
the only one she holds onto.

337
00:42:15,520 --> 00:42:17,840
You can be angry or hate me
however you want,

338
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:21,360
but I really can't abandon her.

339
00:42:24,720 --> 00:42:27,400
I don't want to be cruel
to a woman who's been good to me.

340
00:42:40,640 --> 00:42:42,440
- Sun!
- Aru.

341
00:42:42,520 --> 00:42:43,520
Sun!

342
00:42:44,520 --> 00:42:46,600
Let me stay like this for just a minute.

343
00:42:47,800 --> 00:42:49,120
Just one minute.

344
00:43:05,640 --> 00:43:07,000
Like a couple.

345
00:43:15,640 --> 00:43:18,640
Oh, how did the power go out?

346
00:43:21,280 --> 00:43:22,800
The fuse blew.

347
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:24,520
Then go replace it.

348
00:43:25,120 --> 00:43:26,720
Okay, just a moment.

349
00:43:27,320 --> 00:43:29,320
Miss Nun, take a break.
I'll bring you some water.

350
00:44:25,360 --> 00:44:28,280
Who sent you in here?
This isn't your business.

351
00:44:29,720 --> 00:44:30,960
Mr. Naruban.

352
00:44:35,080 --> 00:44:38,080
Mr. Taiga, the outfit looks amazing.

353
00:44:38,160 --> 00:44:39,440
Thank you.

354
00:44:40,560 --> 00:44:41,440
Mr. Taiga.

355
00:44:42,440 --> 00:44:43,520
Do you like it?

356
00:44:44,920 --> 00:44:45,920
It's okay.

357
00:44:53,760 --> 00:44:56,800
I thought you'd say you like it.

358
00:45:02,520 --> 00:45:04,560
Who let someone unrelated into this room?

359
00:45:22,240 --> 00:45:24,200
{\an8}I want you to be my model.

360
00:45:24,280 --> 00:45:26,960
{\an8}The tears today, they'll turn into a fire

361
00:45:27,680 --> 00:45:31,240
{\an8}that will burn the enemy
until not even a soul remains.

362
00:45:31,320 --> 00:45:32,600
{\an8}<i>Buy his trust first, Rin.</i>

363
00:45:33,880 --> 00:45:35,480
{\an8}<i>Act like bait,</i>

364
00:45:35,560 --> 00:45:39,480
{\an8}<i>draw everything out of him,</i>
<i>then deal with him.</i>

365
00:45:40,920 --> 00:45:41,800
{\an8}Taiga!

366
00:46:11,040 --> 00:46:15,200
Subtitle translation by:
Chomchanach Yanaharn

